{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-257-angular-bisectors","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 257: Sporazum o susednim uglovima","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dati je trougao sa stranicama koje su cijeli brojevi $ABC$, s stranama $a \\le b \\le c$ ($AB = c$, $BC = a$ i $AC = b$).</p>\n<p>Binomije uglova tog trougla se sastaju sa stranicama u tačkama $E$, $F$ i $G$ (videti sliku ispod).</p>\n<img alt=\"trougao ABC, sa simetralama uglova trougla koje se seku sa stranicama u tačkama E, F i G\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/angular-bisectors.gif\" style=\"background-color: white, padding: 10px, display: block, margin-right: auto, margin-left: auto, margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Segменти $EF$, $EG$ na $FG$ delele trougao $ABC$ na četiri manja trougla: $AEG$, $BFE$, $CGF$ i $EFG$. Može se dokazati da je za svaki od ovih četiri trougla, omjer $\\frac{\\text{eneo}(ABC)}{\\text{eneo}(\\text{subtriangle})}$ racionalan broj. Međutim, postoje trouglovi za koje su neki ili svi ovi omjeri cijeli brojevi.</p>\n<p>Koliko trouglova sa stranicama od $≤ 100\\,000\\,000$ postoji da je omjer $\\frac{\\text{eneo}(ABC)}{\\text{eneo}(AEG)}$ cijeli broj?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f46e1000cf542c50ff80","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301905,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-257-angular-bisectors"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function angularBisectors() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nangularBisectors();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>angularBisectors()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>139012411</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(angularBisectors(), 139012411);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-257-angular-bisectors","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-258-a-lagged-fibonacci-sequence","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-256-tatami-free-rooms","id":"5900f46e1000cf542c50ff80","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-257-angular-bisectors"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}